{"data":[{"date":"14:12 02/07","title":"Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, sao Morocco g\u00e2y tai n\u1ea1n ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi?","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/tro-ve-tu-world-cup-2018-sao-morocco-gay-tai-nan-chet-nguoi.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"3939","checkdouble":"190164"},{"date":"14:15 02/07","title":"Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Maradona treo th\u01b0\u1edfng 8.000 b\u1ea3ng truy t\u00ecm k\u1ebb tung tin m\u00ecnh ch\u1ebft","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/vua-bong-da-maradona-treo-thuong-8000-bang-truy-tim-ke-tung-tin-minh-chet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Diego Maradona v\u1eeba treo th\u01b0\u1edfng 8.000 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 truy t\u00ecm k\u1ebb tung tin \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ebft. Trong tr\u1eadn Argentina th\u1eafng Nigeria 2-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Maradona \u0111\u00e3 \u0103n m\u1eebng qu\u00e1 sung t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadp vi\u1ec7n v\u00ec ng\u1ea5t x\u1ec9u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi Maradona \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb, c\u01b0 d\u00e2n m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u00f4n xao b\u1edfi 2 \u0111o\u1ea1n ghi \u00e2m b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c C\u1eadu b\u00e9 v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 qua \u0111\u1eddi. \u0110o\u1ea1n ghi \u00e2m th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i 57 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9t qu\u1ef5 v\u00ec tim m\u1ea1ch. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110o\u1ea1n ghi \u00e2m th\u1ee9 2 xoay quanh vi\u1ec7c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 c\u00e1i ch\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Maradona \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean th\u1ec3 thao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. Ch\u1ec9 trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn, hai \u0111o\u1ea1n ghi \u00e2m v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Maradona \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t qua \u0111\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebb tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/maradona.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c c\u00e0ng di\u1ec5n ra theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i h\u01a1n khi ch\u1ecb g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Maradona \u0111\u00e3 \u0111au kh\u1ed5 t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c suy s\u1ee5p v\u00ec t\u01b0\u1edfng em trai ch\u1ebft th\u1eadt. &ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c, l\u00e0m sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tung tin qu\u00e1i \u00e1c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady&rdquo;. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3 Maradona b\u1ee9c x\u00fac n\u00f3i: &ldquo;T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft&rdquo;. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c C\u1eadu b\u00e9 v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n cho c\u00f4 b\u1ed3 Rocio Oliva c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea5n an m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n s\u1ed1ng ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ng\u1ecfm c\u1ee7 t\u1ecfi nh\u01b0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u00f2n theo lu\u1eadt s\u01b0 ri\u00eang Matias Morla c\u1ee7a Maradona, b\u1ea5t lu\u1eadn v\u00ec nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng phao tin k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 v\u00f4 nh\u00e2n t\u00ednh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00ean \u00e1n. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 danh t\u00ednh k\u1ebb tung tin \u0111\u1ed3n&rdquo;, Matias kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean t\u1edd nh\u1eadt b\u00e1o Clarin, &ldquo;Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi ki\u1ec7n h\u1eafn ta ra t\u00f2a v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi tung tin th\u1ea5t thi\u1ec7t, g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3938","checkdouble":"190165"},{"date":"15:45 02/07","title":"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</h2><h2>HLV HAGL ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec HAGL kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt 1/7, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n song ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n v\u00e0i sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 2, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng d\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \"B\u00e0n thua tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u1eafm. \u1ede hi\u1ec7p 1, hai \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tho\u00e1t thua trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft n\u1eafng n\u00f3ng \u1edf Tam K\u1ef3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhanh ch\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c trong hi\u1ec7p 2. Hai b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ec1u xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb hai bi\u00ean v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Th\u1eadt ti\u1ebfc khi HAGL ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u tung ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi 100% n\u1ed9i binh. Song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu l\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng HAGL n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"Trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, BHL \u0111\u01b0a ra h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 n\u1ed9i binh. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 3 tr\u00ean BXH. L\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 5 v\u1edbi 24 \u0111i\u1ec3m, k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 l\u00e0 Thanh H\u00f3a 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u1ea7n ch\u1eaft chiu h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-quang-nam-22-hagl-cu-dup-cua-van-toan-168-190109.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/van-toan-ghi-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-quang-nam-22-hagl-cu-dup-cua-van-toan-168-190109.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL: C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br />\r\nTi\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/quang-nam-vs-hagl-vleague-2018-372-190082.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/ket-qua-quang-nam-vs-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/quang-nam-vs-hagl-vleague-2018-372-190082.html\">Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL (KT): D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3</span><br />\r\nD\u00f9 c\u00f3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC, tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ebft th\u00fac 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c HAGL ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i chia \u0111i\u1ec3m 2-2 v\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl-168-190063.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dao-rimario-da-co-ben-do-moi-sau-khi-chia-tay-hagl-168-190063.html\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi sau khi chia tay HAGL?</span><br />\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb CLB HAGL thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i V-League. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3937","checkdouble":"190172"},{"date":"16:43 02/07","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 17 V-League: H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/du-am-vong-17-vleague-ha-noi-tien-sat-ngoi-vuong-hagl-chia-diem-dang-tiec.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HAGL ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 V-League.</h2><h2>1. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf khi ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tuy nhi\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng sau 17 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1edbm sau pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh Vinicius \u1edf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 8 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng b\u1eb1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng sau c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 31. 5 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 V\u0103n Ki\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 t\u1edbi h\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ngay t\u1ea1i C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u1edf ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 44 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp sau l\u00e0 Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a BVN \u0111\u1ebfn 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m, m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch qu\u00e1 an to\u00e0n cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 17 V-League H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 17 V-League H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/a00-8311-1530455756.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc 5 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 17 V-League, CLB HAGL c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang gi\u1eef ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Qu\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Claudecir kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1 l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, khi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng, &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng v\u00e0i ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi\u1ebfn HAGL \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi Tam K\u1ef3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f2a tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, CLB HAGL&nbsp;v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Qu\u1ea3ng Nam tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Pleiku \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi 24 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. SLNA l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 6<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 5 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, CLB SLNA kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ed1p 3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn sau v\u00f2ng 17 V-League, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00fang 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, SLNA ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tr\u00ean BXH tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SLNA thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u1eddi gian qua c\u0169ng nh\u1edd v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. Sau hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i L\u1ea1ch Tray b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 3-0&nbsp;\u1edf ph\u00fat 69 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c 3-2 trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i L\u1ea1ch Tray.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e0y, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hai Phong vs SLNA\" title=\"H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs SLNA\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/nhan-dinh-hai-phong-vs-slna-17h00-ngay-17-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>SLNA \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng t\u1ea1i L\u1ea1ch Tray</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. S\u00e0i G\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00eam c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u00edt sao 1-0 nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Thanh H\u00f3a L\u00ea Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 90 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean BXH m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00eam quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a CLB tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng an to\u00e0n. L\u00fac n\u00e0y S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 h\u01a1n TP.HCM 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u1ea1i V-League m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2019.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/1/Highlight-Quang-Ninh-vs-Ha-Noi.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH sau vong 17 V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH sau v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/BXH-sau-vong-17-V-League-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH sau v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-quang-nam-22-hagl-cu-dup-cua-van-toan-168-190109.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/van-toan-ghi-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-quang-nam-22-hagl-cu-dup-cua-van-toan-168-190109.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL: C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\">HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-190140.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-190140.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 thua t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3936","checkdouble":"190182"},{"date":"16:39 02/07","title":"Salah k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Liverpool, t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/salah-chinh-thuc-ky-hop-dong-dai-han-voi-liverpool.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Salah \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2023.</h2><h2>Salah gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Liverpool, Real b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Salah \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool trao cho m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 5 n\u0103m sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSalah \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 44 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng sau khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool t\u1eeb Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36.9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n nh\u01b0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool, t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Salah gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool, t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/salah-chinh-thuc-ky-hop-dong-dai-han-voi-liverpool.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/salah-vi-sao-toi-toa-sang-o-liverpool-172-176203.html\" target=\"_blank\">Salah ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch quan tr\u1ecdng</span> gi\u00fap Liverpool c\u1ea1nh tranh danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQuan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Salah kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Real s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Salah m\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Liverpool. </div>\r\n<h2>Klopp vui m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Salah</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau khi Salah \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Liverpool, HLV Klopp t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0nh cho Salah l\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u00f3 c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n hai \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o Liverpool v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Anfield v\u00e0 th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tham v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Mo Salah cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00e0 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00ec n\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, vi\u1ec7c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y cho th\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn r\u00f5 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Salah v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Salah kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1eadu \u1ea5y cao h\u01a1n l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111o\u1ea1t c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 do c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u1eb1m trong m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mo Salah ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ra sao. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-karius-172-190092.html\">Liverpool \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Karius</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-tro-lai-vu-fekir-quyet-canh-tranh-voi-mu-172-190075.html\">Liverpool tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1ee5 Fekir, quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3935","checkdouble":"190174"},{"date":"16:58 02/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/8/nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-mu-chuan-bi-co-tan-binh-thu-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia Craig Norwood, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tranh th\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 BL\u0110 Man United \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm ch\u1ed1t t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lee Grant \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 do, sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Stoke.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay 35 tu\u1ed5i, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh ra t\u1ea1i Anh n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 3 t\u1ea1i Old Trafford \u2013 sau David De Gea v\u00e0 Sergio Romero. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n cho r\u1eb1ng Grant s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf De Gea ra \u0111i c\u0169ng s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf, khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh T\u00e2y Ban Nha chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, M.U s\u1ebd g\u1eedi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Joel Pereira cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 21 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh mu\u1ed1n CLB cho m\u00ecnh \u0111i \u201cdu h\u1ecdc\u201d. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, M.U c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, n\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o g\u1eedi anh sang \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-MU-chieu-mo-Lee-Grant-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia Craig Norwood, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a CLB \u2013 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh Lee Grant trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Norwood \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 t\u00e2n binh Fred v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot \u2013 ch\u1ec9 1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi CLB \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao 1m93 v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 35 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho Man United. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau, v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Romero \u0111\u1ebfn nay v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia-176-190157.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia-176-190157.html\">M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba Serbia</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Lazio.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu-172-190097.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu-172-190097.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Martial n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi MU?</span><br>\r\nBayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Old Trafford nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool-172-190006.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool-172-190006.html\">MU mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t The Kop, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi \u0111\u1ee7 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3934","checkdouble":"190176"},{"date":"16:56 02/07","title":"Salah gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p t\u1eeb Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/hlv-klopp-phat-bieu-ve-viec-salah-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a The Kop trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Salah g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi Liverpool</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGia nh\u1eadp Liverpool t\u1eeb AS Roma \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp. Anh ghi t\u1edbi 44 b\u00e0n sau 52 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng bao g\u1ed3m 32 t\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSalah l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Liverpool c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong t\u1ed1p 4 c\u1ee7a Premier League. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid, n\u01a1i anh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n t\u1eeb s\u1edbm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/HLV-Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Salah-va-viec-gia-han-hop-dong--hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Salah gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi m\u00f9a 2017/18 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Salah. T\u1eeb Barcelona t\u1edbi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ebfp h\u00e0ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n Anfield \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ai C\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0ng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u1eb3n khi\u1ebfn hai g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 n\u00e0y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, Salah \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00e0 trong \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. C\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01a1n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ra \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u1ee7a CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vui m\u1eebng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 vi\u1ec7c Salah gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u201cMessi ch\u00e2u Phi\u201d cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1eedi \u0111i tham v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp\" title=\"Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/liverpool-da-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-chieu-mo-tan-binh-thu-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 CLB trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d, HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah tr\u00ean trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u00f3 c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n 2 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng: Ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i Anfield, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u00f9ng nhau \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Salah cam k\u1ebft v\u00e0 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng n\u01a1i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u00fd ngh\u0129a. V\u00e0 khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Salah s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Mo Salah tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/salah-va-cac-dong-doi-bi-cdv-nha-si-nhuc-421-189641.html\">Salah v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecb C\u0110V nh\u00e0 s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/salah-nhan-loi-sau-chien-dich-world-cup-tham-hoa-cua-ai-cap-469-189567.html\">Salah nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-salah-tro-thanh-cong-dan-danh-du-o-chechnya-188-189341.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Salah tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n danh d\u1ef1 \u1edf Chechnya</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/salah-len-tieng-sau-khi-ai-cap-som-bi-loai-khoi-world-cup-421-189235.html\">Salah l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau khi Ai C\u1eadp s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3933","checkdouble":"190179"},{"date":"17:30 02/07","title":"\"Mourinho \u0111ang ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Pogba v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec9nh cao\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/23/mourinho-dang-ngan-can-pogba-vuon-toi-dinh-cao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jeremie Aliadiere kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pogba v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 v\u00ec Mourinho.</h2><h2>Pogba ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng khi \u0111\u01b0a Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford h\u00e8 2016. Sau 4 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Juventus, Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/pogba-len-tieng-dap-tra-nhung-chi-trich-172-187755.html\" target=\"_blank\">ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</span>. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mournho v\u00e0 c\u0169ng nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00ecm h\u00e3m Pogba \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00ecm h\u00e3m Pogba \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Mourinho-dang-kim-ham-Pogba-o-MU-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Aliadiere cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00ecm h\u00e3m Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aliadiere \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Pogba trong th\u1eddi gian qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 cho Pogba khi HLV kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n. V\u00e0 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 n\u0103m tr\u1eddi. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1i ki\u1ec3u \u2018t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a \u1edf Man United nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 cho Ph\u00e1p\u2019.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i nh\u1edb khi Pogba \u1edf Juventus, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Man United, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c Mourinho kh\u00f4ng trao cho Pogba nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 duy tr\u00ec vi\u1ec7c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba m\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Pogba trong l\u00f2ng NHM Man United c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. S\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn, Pogba mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i t\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec\u201d, Aliadiere n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn 100% s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina nh\u1edd t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xung quanh ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng khi ch\u00fang ta th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n Pogba, c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean nhanh ch\u00f3ng th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Pogba:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-tang-boc-mbappe-len-may-sau-tran-dai-thang-argentina-469-190086.html\">Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng Mbappe</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-phan-phao-truoc-nhung-chi-trich-cua-cdv-phap-469-189872.html\">Pogba ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3932","checkdouble":"190183"},{"date":"09:51 02/07","title":"M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \"Pogba Serbia\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/16/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Lazio.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus quan t\u00e2m Sergej Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Juventus-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic-dang-rat-kho-khan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Lazio, anh ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, anh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Serie A c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Juventus. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/doi-bong-cua-serie-a-bat-ngo-hoi-mua-sao-khung-arsenal-172-189741.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lazio quan t\u00e2m Ramsey</span> c\u1ee7a Arsenal cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Lazio.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/Lazio-muon-mua-Aaron-Ramsey-thay-Milinkovic-Savic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Lazio d\u00e0nh cho Milinkovic-Savic khi\u1ebfn Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, theo Tuttosport, Lazio \u0111\u00f2i 100 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ed9ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rodrigo Bentancur m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, n\u1ebfu Juventus kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u00e0 Juventus g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat lui trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 80 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n MU, PSG v\u00e0 Barca l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn m\u00e0 Lazio y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Milinkovic-Savic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3931","checkdouble":"190157"},{"date":"09:55 02/07","title":"\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/marlon-chuan-bi-gia-nhap-southampton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Barcelona c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn CLB c\u1ee7a Premier League v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Marlon kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Barca</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarlon t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Marlon Santos da Silva Barbosa, sinh ng\u00e0y 7 th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m 1995. Anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Barcelona t\u1eeb Fluminense d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2016/17. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb, trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Blaugrana k\u00fd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng do kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi Ernesto Valverde, Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em Marlon cho Nice c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Fluminense m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton t\u1eeb Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton t\u1eeb Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/marlon-chuan-bi-gia-nhap-southampton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton t\u1eeb Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNice kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Marlon v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 anh l\u1ea1i Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 Valverde v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Southampton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Marlon c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Barca. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Premier League n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u00e0 Southampton v\u00e0 West Ham \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Blaugrana.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Marlon chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Southampton. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n Nam n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i. Trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Marlon s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Southampton ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a CLB n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Marlon s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Southampton h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Stuart Armstrong t\u1eeb Celtic v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Basler Mohamed Elyounoussi t\u1eeb Basel. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, The Saints \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn Andrea Petagna c\u1ee7a Atalanta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-barca-172-189954.html\">Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/rafinha-muon-roi-barca-cang-som-cang-tot-180-189772.html\">Sao Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018-172-189666.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Neymar sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia-180-189646.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pogba Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-va-real-dai-chien-vi-sao-bayern-munich-180-189512.html\">Barca v\u00e0 Real \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3930","checkdouble":"190156"},{"date":"10:58 02/07","title":"Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/11/real-madrid-da-co-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Luka Modric d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 BL\u0110 Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Modric</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Toni Kroos h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Tuong-lai-Luka-Modric-da-duoc-quyet-dinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luka Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn cho Real Madrid, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 theo \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Don Balon, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/bayern-munich-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-sao-real-madrid-180-189278.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Luka Modric</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tottenham v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1edd Mirror c\u1ee7a Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 40 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Luka Modric d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 BL\u0110 Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Modric\" title=\"tien ve Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/real-madrid-da-co-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n40 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng si\u00eau l\u00f2ng, nh\u01b0ng Real Madrid th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng. HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Modric v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sergio Ramos c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Real Madrid b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, anh tin r\u1eb1ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Modric v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Modric \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf Nga. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3929","checkdouble":"190162"},{"date":"09:34 02/07","title":"Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201ckh\u1eafc tinh\u201d c\u1ee7a Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/15/barca-muon-mua-kante-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y lu\u00f4n g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho Messi. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Argentina t\u1ea1i World Cup.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kante l\u00e0 kh\u1eafc tinh c\u1ee7a Messi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2016/17, N'Golo Kante kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. S\u1ee9c c\u00e0n qu\u00e9t, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 qua 2 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Barcelona m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Kante \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 theo k\u00e8m si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi. D\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Leicester, ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Barca kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, kh\u1eafc tinh c\u1ee7a Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, kh\u1eafc tinh c\u1ee7a Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Barca-muon-mua-Kante-cua-Chelsea,-khac-tinh-cua-Messi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kante khi\u1ebfn Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y th\u00f4i, khi g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Kante ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Messi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u00ean ph\u00eda Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Argentina m\u1ea5t h\u00fat trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9i s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng khu trung tuy\u1ebfn, Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Eric Abidal, \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. T\u1edd Don Balon cho hay nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Barca bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Lionel Messi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante\" title=\"Kante\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/15/barca-muon-mua-kante-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, Tiki-Taka v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i l\u00e0 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Barca. Nh\u01b0ng trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Messi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t ngay c\u1ea3 khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t Kante c\u00e0y \u1ea3i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf trung tuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eeba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Ernesto Valverde, Barca c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. Ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 Paulinho v\u00e0 Nelson Semedo cho Blaugrana \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-khong-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-189958.html\">G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng mua Willian, Barca v\u1eabn b\u1ecb Chelsea kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-barca-172-189954.html\">Liverpool nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/rafinha-muon-roi-barca-cang-som-cang-tot-180-189772.html\">Sao Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018-172-189666.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Neymar sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3928","checkdouble":"190155"},{"date":"10:55 02/07","title":"Ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i khuy\u00ean Gareth Bale b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/1/gareth-bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-real-ve-voi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi M.U \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng vinh quang m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh M.U v\u00e0 \u0110T x\u1ee9 Wales, Mickey Thomas.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bale mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid, Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 1 La Liga v\u00e0 4 Champions League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales mong mu\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1eady. Ngay sau khi c\u00f9ng Real \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i Champions League m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 th\u00e1ng, anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBale mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea1i Real. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 6 th\u00f4i, Jonathan Barnett - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Bale c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tottenham n\u00f3i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/Gareth-Bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-Real-ve-voi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bale c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay Real Madrid h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean r\u1eddi b\u1ecf Real</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi \u201cC\u01a1n l\u1ed1c x\u1ee9 Wales\u201d bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Bayern Munich c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi M.U v\u00e0 Premier League. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 M.U v\u00e0 x\u1ee9 Wales: Mickey Thomas.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGareth Bale kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau\u201d, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 63 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i. \u201cCV c\u1ee7a Bale \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. T\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Bale \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. N\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale\" title=\"Bale\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/gareth-bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-real-ve-voi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean b\u1ecf Real v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u1ea1i Premier League</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan United, Chelsea r\u1ed3i Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd t\u1edbi Gareth Bale. V\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i Thomas tin \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi l\u00fac h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i Premier League. \u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng may, Bale \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Neymar ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Anh v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, gi\u00e0nh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u, Bale s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i cho Bayern Munich, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi l\u00fac ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh \u1edf Premier League.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ryan-giggs-khuyen-mourinho-ky-hop-dong-voi-sao-real-madrid-172-189040.html\">Ryan Giggs khuy\u00ean Mourinho k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi sao Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-united-chuan-bi-dua-gareth-bale-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi-172-188500.html\">Man United chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0a Gareth Bale l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u201ckh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-tuong-lai-ronaldo-va-bale-nuong-nhau-ma-song-180-188128.html\">Chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo v\u00e0 Bale: N\u01b0\u01a1ng nhau m\u00e0 s\u1ed1ng!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/bo-vo-tuong-lai-bi-cam-tham-du-dam-cuoi-cua-bale-188-187786.html\">B\u1ed1 v\u1ee3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1m c\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Bale</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-moi-goi-gareth-bale-den-old-trafford-172-187570.html\">C\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Gareth Bale \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3927","checkdouble":"190161"}]}